    "body": "I definitely agree with @alexcrichton's intuiton here.\n\nOne true stability doesn't seem good for anyone, but I'd also prefer stability to be inherited by default in re-exports. So we don't need to annotate all re-exports. Only the ones that we want to.\n\nI'm a bit on the fence about stable of unstable. My gut reaction is that it _could_ be useful, and I can't imagine it would be a big problem?\n",
